text: Andrea Harsági (born 22 March 1971) is a Hungarian badminton player. She competed in women's singles at the 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of Hungary Category:Badminton players at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Nyíregyháza
